  <brief_title>Chemoradiotherapy Sequenced Radical Surgery for Colorectal Cancer With PALNM</brief_title>
  <official_title>Concurrent Chemoradiotherapy Sequenced Radical Surgery for Para-aortic Lymph Node Metastasis of Left-sided Colon and Rectal Cancer</official_title>
